now, from the definition (\ref{CMatrix}),%
\begin{equation}
\left\{  C_{j},A_{mn}\right\}  _{PB}+\left\{  C_{m},A_{nj}\right\}
_{PB}+\left\{  C_{n},A_{jm}\right\}  _{PB}=0
\end{equation}
